{"tid":1795186,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"平安夜好去處：尖沙咀文物探知館「聖山遺粹：啟德地區出土宋元文物展」","createTime":"2019-12-23T16:42:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T14:38:58.000Z","uid":7439,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9a332450c547f04ed9f116020c4d6048a8ad1603","tid":1795186,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:42:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201912/23/P2019122300279_photo_1169639.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201912%2F23%2FP2019122300279_photo_1169639.jpg&h=5c240fcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201912/23/P2019122300279_photo_1169618.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201912%2F23%2FP2019122300279_photo_1169618.jpg&h=be7827d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n文物探知館舉辦「聖山遺粹：啟德地區出土宋元文物展」（附圖）<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  香港文物探知館明日（十二月二十四日）起至二○二○年二月二十六日舉辦「聖山遺粹：啟德地區出土宋元文物展」，展出約二百組啟德地區出土的考古文物。<br />\n<br />\n  展覽的開幕典禮今日（十二月二十三日）舉行，由古物諮詢委員會主席蘇彰德、發展局文物保育專員任浩晨和古物古蹟辦事處執行秘書蕭麗娟主禮。<br />\n   <br />\n  隨着啟德機場於一九九八年關閉，啟德新發展區的規劃為九龍灣聖山遺址一帶提供了考古研究的契機，並發現了豐富的宋元時期文化遺存，包括大量產自浙江、福建及江西不同窰口的陶瓷製品。同時期的相類似瓷器也曾外銷，不少可於當時海上陶瓷之路沿線的沉船上發現。今次展覽可讓參觀人士了解九龍灣一帶在宋元時期的經濟發展、海上貿易和百姓的生活面貌。<br />\n   <br />\n  展覽的重點展品包括龍泉窰出產的「青釉八卦紋香爐」和「青釉雙魚洗」；磁灶窰出產的「褐釉龍紋繫罐」、「綠釉鳳紋盤」；以及「大觀通寶」銅錢。展覽亦同時展出由香港中文大學文物館借出的同期陶瓷文物。<br />\n   <br />\n  展覽由古物古蹟辦事處籌劃，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">免費入場</span></span>。詳情可瀏覽古物古蹟辦事處網頁（<a href=\"http://www.amo.gov.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amo.gov.hk&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpq2paxXJRTFpYESBXKIXFX0%3D&h=d9453e9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.amo.gov.hk</a>）或致電2208 4400。<br />\n<br />\n  香港文物探知館位於尖沙咀海防道九龍公園。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年12月23日（星期一）<br />\n香港時間15時48分<br />\n<br />\n開放時間<br />\n星期一至三、星期五：10:00-18:00<br />\n星期六、日及公眾假期: 10:00-19:00<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">聖誕節前夕（12月24日）及農曆年除夕：10:00-17:00</span><br />\n星期四（公眾假期除外）、農曆年初一及年初二：休息"},{"pid":"f976ddfb661db3f1b6908e419c589b9eba2e60ff","tid":1795186,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:43:51.000Z","msg":"香港文物探知館（英語：Hong Kong Heritage Discovery Centre），香港康樂及文化事務署轄下古物古蹟辦事處的一座展覽館，位於香港油尖旺區九龍公園園內。香港文物探知館展示香港的文物建築專題及最新的考古發現等；該館亦經常有舉辦專題講座、工作坊及導賞活動等，以促進大眾，尤其是學生對香港文物的認識。館內有專題展覽廳、演講廳、教育活動室及參考圖書館等設施。其中專題展覽廳入口的銅門，是第三代香港滙豐總行大廈（1983年拆卸重建）的大門。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.discoverhongkong.com/tc/images/see-do/culture-heritage/large/1.4.4.3.2-The-Hong-Kong-Heritage-Discovery-Centre_03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.discoverhongkong.com%2Ftc%2Fimages%2Fsee-do%2Fculture-heritage%2Flarge%2F1.4.4.3.2-The-Hong-Kong-Heritage-Discovery-Centre_03.jpg&h=6c8e610a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n該建築前身是威菲路軍營S61及S62座，於1910年落成。1970年軍營改建為九龍公園，這兩幢建築於1983年成為香港歷史博物館的臨時館址，至1998年香港歷史博物館遷出。其後這兩幢建築物一直空置，後幾文物復修工程，成為今日古物古蹟辦事處的文物探知館，於2005年10月正式開放。"},{"pid":"abc644199edd99c1a5421663c6456f7ccfc052a9","tid":1795186,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:44:01.000Z","msg":"如何前往<br />\n從港鐵尖沙咀站A1出口，沿海防道右轉進入九龍公園。香港文物探知館位於公園的鳥湖旁邊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8279e6efcfef17dfabe244bfe4744c6e25e6be0","tid":1795186,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:44:28.000Z","msg":"想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a11421b47780bcf4fc55a3fbb3f8684d43895c6c","tid":1795186,"uid":164751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:46:07.000Z","msg":"好提議<br />\n有益"},{"pid":"f51b95b9ec59e3ed71455f44548ba81f3e84e306","tid":1795186,"uid":163704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:46:15.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[我終於搵到FC撚嘅歸屬地] 已經整好左個搜尋器，而家要大家俾意見想要有咩類別<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1794463\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1794463</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"59997f252fb1336be654189027273317027108f2","tid":1795186,"uid":282490,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:46:26.000Z","msg":"有個做地盤嘅uncle <br />\n<br />\n尋日傾計問佢做地盤嘅趣事<br />\n<br />\n佢話喺啟德地盤掘掘下泥，掘到瓦片陶瓷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1153b31c7b755595303de7e87ee10f97e02cef26","tid":1795186,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:51:58.000Z","msg":"九龍公園仲有個咩衛生防護展覽館<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該係海防道一入去左下角"},{"pid":"526f25ac2737a825a54e98fa5277146db949d816","tid":1795186,"uid":302475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59997f252fb1336be654189027273317027108f2","tid":1795186,"uid":282490,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:46:26.000Z","msg":"有個做地盤嘅uncle <br />\n<br />\n尋日傾計問佢做地盤嘅趣事<br />\n<br />\n佢話喺啟德地盤掘掘下泥，掘到瓦片陶瓷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:55:56.000Z","msg":"唔小心撈埋考古<br />\n正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f61196798700aea9c6e0c55744f3a6e3ca632f2","tid":1795186,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8279e6efcfef17dfabe244bfe4744c6e25e6be0","tid":1795186,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:44:28.000Z","msg":"想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T17:10:37.000Z","msg":"go"},{"pid":"d8da235cb02d93ff7694df40e607c41df3b479b9","tid":1795186,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T17:55:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa4e09913b19c0ffccf5680624d28bd0c8d6223f","tid":1795186,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T02:40:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ee5da271a56d0e490c3c6df423579d8527a8a1","tid":1795186,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1153b31c7b755595303de7e87ee10f97e02cef26","tid":1795186,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:51:58.000Z","msg":"九龍公園仲有個咩衛生防護展覽館<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該係海防道一入去左下角"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T04:24:22.000Z","msg":"衞生教育展覽及資料中心位於九龍尖沙咀九龍公園S4座內，於一九九七年五月十七日正式啟用。<br />\n<br />\n中心設有一個展覽廳，位於一幢逾百年歷史的建築物內，並佔用兩個樓層，面積達1,100平方米。此外，中心還有一個佔地400平方米的戶外衞生教育花園、一個藏有4,500多本刊物的資料中心、一個可容納60人的演講室及一個供該中心職員使用的辦公室。<br />\n<br />\n地址：<br />\n九龍尖沙咀九龍公園S4座(位於九龍公園內，近海防道與彌敦道交界處，尖沙咀港鐵站A1出口。)<br />\n<br />\n開放時間：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">星期二、三、五及六：上午8時45分至下午6時15分</span><br />\n星期日：上午11時至下午9時<br />\n星期一、四及公眾假期︰休息<br />\n<br />\n入場費：<br />\n全免"},{"pid":"0e7c895444c1a69940fd8ad101b9a22202b1704f","tid":1795186,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T04:40:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"